decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.filterTR.loop\">List.filterTR.loop</a> <span class=\"fn\">p</span> <span class=\"fn\">as</span> <span class=\"fn\">bs</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">bs</span>.reverse</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HAppend.hAppend\">++</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.filter\">List.filter</a> <span class=\"fn\">p</span> <span class=\"fn\">as</span></span></span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/df668f00e6c08cb63661aacc43d0e83388e2c60d/src/Init/Data/List/Basic.lean#L273-L277","name":"List.filterTR.loop","line":273,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.filterTR.loop","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.filterTR.loop\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">filterTR</span>.<span class=\"name\">loop</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{α : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(p : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/df668f00e6c08cb63661aacc43d0e83388e2c60d/src/Init/Data/List/Basic.lean#L270-L277","name":"List.filterTR","line":270,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.filterTR","doc":"Tail-recursive version of `List.filter`. "},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.filterTR\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">filterTR</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{α : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(p : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(as : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/df668f00e6c08cb63661aacc43d0e83388e2c60d/src/Init/Data/List/Basic.lean#L263-L267","name":"List.filter","line":263,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.filter","doc":"`O(|l|)`. `filter f l` returns the list of elements in `l` for which `f` returns true.\n```\nfilter (· > 2) [1, 2, 5, 2, 7, 7] = [5, 7, 7]\n```\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.filter\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">filter</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{α : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(p : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/df668f00e6c08cb63661aacc43d0e83388e2c60d/src/Init/Data/List/Basic.lean#L250-L255","name":"List.filterMap","line":250,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.filterMap","doc":"`O(|l|)`. `filterMap f l` takes a function `f : α → Option β` and applies it to each element of `l`;\nthe resulting non-`none` values are collected to form the output list.\n```\nfilterMap\n  (fun x => if x > 2 then some (2 * x) else none)\n  [1, 2, 5, 2, 7, 7]\n= [10, 14, 14]\n```\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.filterMap\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">filterMap</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{α : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{β : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> v}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(f : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <span class=\"fn\">β</span></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">β</span></span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/df668f00e6c08cb63661aacc43d0e83388e2c60d/src/Init/Data/List/Basic.lean#L236-L238","name":"List.join","line":236,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.join","doc":"`O(|join L|)`. `join L` concatenates all the lists in `L` into one list.\n* `join [[a], [], [b, c], [d, e, f]] = [a, b, c, d, e, f]`\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.join\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">join</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{α : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>)</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/df668f00e6c08cb63661aacc43d0e83388e2c60d/src/Init/Data/List/Basic.lean#L228-L230","name":"List.map_eq_mapTR","line":228,"kind":"theorem","docLink":"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.map_eq_mapTR","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.map_eq_mapTR\"><span class=\"name\">List</span>.<span class=\"name\">map_eq_mapTR</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.map\">@<a href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.map\">List.map</a></a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <a href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.mapTR\">